import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`A physical location with a fixed address where one or more Real Estate Agent's work`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://schema.org/Organization"}}>{`https://schema.org/Organization`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example"}}>{`Example`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`# note: any string value may also be an array of string
# JSON-LD parsers may be configured to reduce single value arrays to direct values
# feedback wanted: would you prefer to always get array values for consistent parsing
# or shrinking single element arrays vor readability?
   
type: RealEstateOffice
id: 'https://officeid.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'  
name: Gotham City Properties
url: 'https://example.com/office/gotham_city'
email: 'info@example.com'
faxNumber: '867-5309'
telephone: '867-5309'
address:
  type: PostalAddress
  streetAddress:
    - 1 Wayne Manor Drive
    - Cave Entrance
  addressLocality: Gotham City
  addressRegion: Gotham
  addressCountry: Marvel
  postalCode: 12345
  
contactPoint:
- 
  type: ContactPoint
  name: REO
  email: REOEmail
- 
  type: ContactPoint
  name: Referral
  email: ReferralEmail
- 
  type: ContactPoint
  name: Relocation
  email: RelocationEmail
  faxNumber: RelocationFax
  telephone:
  - '(000) 867-5309'
  url: RelocationWebsite
  
memberOf:
-
  type: OrganizationRole
  roleName: MLSMember
  memberId: OfficeMLSID1
  memberOf:
    type: MultipleListingService
    name: OfficeMLSName1
  member: 'https://officeid.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
-
  type: OrganizationRole
  roleName: MLSMember
  memberId: OfficeMLSID15
  memberOf:
    type: MultipleListingService
    name: OfficeMLSName15
  member: 'https://officeid.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
-
  type: OrganizationRole
  roleName: DesignationType
  startDate: '2018-02-19T13:24:18.557'

parentOrganization:
  type: Organization
  identifier:
    AffiliateGUID: affiliat-e591-e811-9efd-0a3d083f1533
    AffiliateID: AffiliateID

# Context specific values

additionalProperty:
  '@context': 'https://yodata.io/hsf/reflex/context#'
  BrokerID: BrokerID
  OfficeType: OfficeType
  OfficeStatus: OfficeStatus
  isActive: IsActive
  Continent: Continent
  FullTimeAgents: 1
  PartTimeAgents: 1
  PrimaryContact: PrimaryContact
  OfficeEffectiveDate: OfficeEffectiveDate
  REOEmailCheck: REOEmailCheck
  ReferralEmailCheck: ReferralEmailCheck
  RelocationEmailCheck: RelocationEmailCheck
  Specialty: Specialty
  TimeIn: '1970-01-01T00:00:00.000'
  TimeUpdated: '1970-01-01T00:00:00.000'
  RelocationOffice: RelocationOffice
  
identifier:
 '@context': 'https://yodata.io/hsf/reflex/context#'
 OfficeGUID: officed6-d591-e811-9efd-0a3d083f1533OfficeGUID
 OfficeID: OfficeID
 OfficeId: OfficeId
 OfficeMLSID: OfficeMLSID
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example---json"}}>{`Example - JSON`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-json"}}>{`{
